These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: tram, train, taxi, car, ship, subway
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, house, jazz, r&b, rock, soul
 1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
 4. the fan of soul is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 5. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the fan of rock##5
 6. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the person driving the subway##7
 7. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the fan of jazz##8
 8. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 9. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
10. the fan of classical is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
11. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
12. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the car##1
13. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
14. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the fan of house and the person driving the taxi##7
15. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
16. the person driving the ship is not the fan of r&b##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Transport           | car | train | tram | ship | subway | taxi |
| Music-Genre   | classical | jazz    | house  | rock  | r&b            | soul  |

