.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, british, canadian, polish, spanish
There are 6 different favourite colors: azure, ivory, ebony, green, emerald, yellow
 1. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 2. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
 3. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 4. the person who likes ebony is not to the left of the argentine##8
 5. the british is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
 6. the spanish is on the left or right of the british##3
 7. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 8. the canadian is not to the right of the canadian##8
 9. the american is somewhere to the right of the british##5
10. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes yellow is somewhere between the polish and the person who likes ebony##7
12. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
13. the spanish is between the person who likes emerald and the person who likes yellow##2
14. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
15. the person who likes ebony is somewhere between the person who likes yellow and the american##7
16. the person who likes emerald is not to the left of the person who likes emerald##8
17. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
18. the polish is the person who likes ivory##1
19. the person who likes ebony is not the american##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
| Nationality   | polish   | british | spanish    | canadian      | argentine | american |
| Color         | ivory | emerald  | azure | yellow | ebony   | green  |

