 5. the american is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the polish is between the argentine and the dutch##2
 7. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the dutch##8
 8. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the argentine##3
10. the person drinking fanta is not the american##6
11. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the american##5
12. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the polish##3
13. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | italian | dutch  | polish     | argentine | american |
| Beverage           | milk        | lemonade    | sprite | 7up | fanta     | cola  |

